msgid "# Versioning Policy"
msgstr "# 版本策略"

msgid ""
"Starting with vLLM 0.7.x, the vLLM Ascend Plugin ([vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend)) project follows [PEP "
"440](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/) to publish versions matching vLLM "
"([vllm-project/vllm](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm))."
msgstr ""
"从 vLLM 0.7.x 开始，vLLM Ascend 插件（[vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend)）项目遵循 [PEP "
"440](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/) 发布与 vLLM（[vllm-"
"project/vllm](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm)）匹配的版本。"

msgid "## vLLM Ascend Plugin versions"
msgstr "## vLLM Ascend 插件版本"

msgid ""
"Each vLLM Ascend release is versioned as `v[major].[minor].[micro][rcN][.postN]` (such as\n"
"`v0.7.3rc1`, `v0.7.3`, `v0.7.3.post1`)"
msgstr ""
"每个 vLLM Ascend 版本均采用 `v[主版本].[次版本].[修订号][rcN][.postN]` 格式进行版本命名（例如\n"
"`v0.7.3rc1`、`v0.7.3`、`v0.7.3.post1`）"

msgid ""
"- **Final releases**: Typically scheduled every three months, with careful alignment to the vLLM upstream release cycle and the Ascend software product roadmap.\n"
"- **Pre releases**: Typically issued **on demand**, labeled with rcN to indicate the Nth release candidate. They are intended to support early testing by users ahead of the final release.\n"
"- **Post releases**: Typically issued **on demand** to address minor errors in a final release. Different from [PEP-440 post release note](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/#post-releases) convention, these versions include actual bug fixes, as the final release version must strictly align with the vLLM final release format (`v[major].[minor].[micro]`). Any post version must be published as a patch version of the final release."
msgstr ""
"- **正式版本**：通常每三个月发布一次，并与 vLLM 上游发布周期及 Ascend 软件产品路线图保持严格对齐。\n"
"- **预发布版本**：通常**按需**发布，以 rcN 标记表示第 N 个候选版本。旨在支持用户在正式版本发布前进行早期测试。\n"
"- **补丁版本**：通常**按需**发布，用于修复正式版本中的小错误。与 [PEP-440 补丁版本说明](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/#post-releases) 的惯例不同，这些版本包含实际的错误修复，因为正式版本必须严格遵循 vLLM 正式版本格式（`v[主版本].[次版本].[修订号]`）。任何补丁版本都必须作为正式版本的补丁版本发布。"

msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

msgid ""
"- `v0.7.x`: first final release to match the vLLM `v0.7.x` version.\n"
"- `v0.7.3rc1`: first pre version of vLLM Ascend.\n"
"- `v0.7.3.post1`: post release for the `v0.7.3` release if it has some minor errors."
msgstr ""
"- `v0.7.x`：首个与 vLLM `v0.7.x` 版本匹配的正式版本。\n"
"- `v0.7.3rc1`：vLLM Ascend 的首个预发布版本。\n"
"- `v0.7.3.post1`：针对 `v0.7.3` 版本存在小错误时的补丁版本。"

msgid "## Release compatibility matrix"
msgstr "## 版本兼容性矩阵"

msgid ""
"The table below is the release compatibility matrix for vLLM Ascend release."
msgstr "下表为 vLLM Ascend 版本的版本兼容性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"If you're using v0.7.3, don't forget to install [mindie-"
"turbo](https://pypi.org/project/mindie-turbo) as well."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用的是 v0.7.3，请不要忘记同时安装 [mindie-turbo](https://pypi.org/project/mindie-"
"turbo)。"

msgid ""
"For main branch of vLLM Ascend, we usually make it compatible with the "
"latest vLLM release and a newer commit hash of vLLM. Please note that this "
"table is usually updated. Please check it regularly."
msgstr ""
"对于 vLLM Ascend 的 main 分支，我们通常使其与最新的 vLLM 版本以及更新的 vLLM "
"提交哈希兼容。请注意，此表格会定期更新，请定期查看。"

msgid "## Release cadence"
msgstr "## 发布节奏"

msgid "### Release window"
msgstr "### 发布窗口"

msgid "## Branch policy"
msgstr "## 分支策略"

msgid "vLLM Ascend includes two branches: main and dev."
msgstr "vLLM Ascend 包含两个分支：main 和 dev。"

msgid ""
"- **main**: corresponds to the vLLM main branch and latest 1 or 2 release version. It is continuously monitored for quality through Ascend CI.\n"
"- **releases/vX.Y.Z**: development branch, created with part of new releases of vLLM. For example, `releases/v0.13.0` is the dev branch for vLLM `v0.13.0` version."
msgstr ""
"- **main**：对应 vLLM 主分支及最新的 1 或 2 个发布版本。通过 Ascend CI 持续监控其质量。\n"
"- **releases/vX.Y.Z**：开发分支，随 vLLM 的部分新版本创建。例如，`releases/v0.13.0` 是 vLLM `v0.13.0` 版本的开发分支。"

msgid ""
"Commits should typically be merged into the main branch first, and only then"
" backported to the dev branch, to reduce maintenance costs as much as "
"possible."
msgstr "提交通常应首先合并到 main 分支，然后再反向移植到 dev 分支，以尽可能降低维护成本。"

msgid "### Maintenance branch and EOL"
msgstr "### 维护分支与生命周期终止 (EOL)"

msgid "The table below lists branch states."
msgstr "下表列出了分支状态。"

msgid "### Branch states"
msgstr "### 分支状态"

msgid ""
"Note that vLLM Ascend will only be released for a certain vLLM release "
"version, not for every version. Hence, you may notice that some versions "
"have corresponding dev branches (e.g. `releases/v0.13.0`), while others do "
"not (e.g. `releases/v0.12.0`). The vLLM Ascend release branch now follows "
"the `releases/vX.Y.Z` naming convention, replacing the previous `vX.Y.Z-dev`"
" format to align with vLLM's branch naming standards."
msgstr ""
"请注意，vLLM Ascend 仅针对特定的 vLLM 发布版本进行发布，而非每个版本。因此，您可能会注意到某些版本有对应的开发分支（例如 "
"`releases/v0.13.0`），而其他版本则没有（例如 `releases/v0.12.0`）。vLLM Ascend 发布分支现在遵循 "
"`releases/vX.Y.Z` 命名约定，取代了之前的 `vX.Y.Z-dev` 格式，以与 vLLM 的分支命名标准保持一致。"

msgid ""
"Usually, each minor version of vLLM (such as 0.7) corresponds to a vLLM "
"Ascend version branch and supports its latest version (such as 0.7.3), as "
"shown below:"
msgstr "通常，vLLM 的每个次要版本（例如 0.7）对应一个 vLLM Ascend 版本分支，并支持其最新版本（例如 0.7.3），如下所示："

msgid "### Feature branches"
msgstr "### 特性分支"

msgid ""
"- Branch: The feature branch should be created with a prefix `rfc/` followed by the feature name, such as `rfc/feature-name`.\n"
"- State: The state of the feature branch is `Maintained` until it is merged into the main branch or deleted.\n"
"- RFC Link: The feature branch should be created with a corresponding RFC issue. The creation of a feature branch requires an RFC and approval from at least two maintainers.\n"
"- Scheduled Merge Time: The final goal of a feature branch is to be merged into the main branch. If it remains unmerged for more than three months, the mentor maintainer should evaluate whether to delete the branch.\n"
"- Mentor: The mentor should be a vLLM Ascend maintainer who is responsible for the feature branch."
msgstr ""
"- 分支：特性分支应以 `rfc/` 为前缀，后跟特性名称，例如 `rfc/feature-name`。\n"
"- 状态：特性分支在被合并到主分支或删除之前，其状态为 `Maintained`。\n"
"- RFC 链接：特性分支应创建对应的 RFC 议题。创建特性分支需要一份 RFC 并获得至少两位维护者的批准。\n"
"- 计划合并时间：特性分支的最终目标是合并到主分支。如果超过三个月仍未合并，导师维护者应评估是否删除该分支。\n"
"- 导师：导师应为 vLLM Ascend 的维护者，负责该特性分支。"

msgid "### Backward compatibility"
msgstr "### 向后兼容性"

msgid ""
"For main branch, vLLM Ascend should work with vLLM main branch and latest 1 "
"or 2 releases. To ensure backward compatibility, do as follows:"
msgstr "对于主分支，vLLM Ascend 应与 vLLM 主分支及最新的 1 到 2 个版本兼容。为确保向后兼容性，请执行以下操作："

msgid ""
"- Both main branch and target vLLM release, such as the vLLM main branch and vLLM 0.8.4, are tested by Ascend E2E CI.\n"
"- To make sure that code changes are compatible with the latest 1 or 2 vLLM releases, vLLM Ascend introduces a version check mechanism inside the code. It checks the version of the installed vLLM package first to decide which code logic to use. If users hit the `InvalidVersion` error, it may indicate that they have installed a dev or editable version of vLLM package. In this case, we provide the env variable `VLLM_VERSION` to let users specify the version of vLLM package to use.\n"
"- Document changes should be compatible with the latest 1 or 2 vLLM releases. Notes should be added if there are any breaking changes."
msgstr ""
"- 主分支和目标 vLLM 版本（例如 vLLM 主分支和 vLLM 0.8.4）均需通过 Ascend E2E CI 测试。\n"
"- 为确保代码更改与最新的 1 到 2 个 vLLM 版本兼容，vLLM Ascend 在代码中引入了版本检查机制。它首先检查已安装的 vLLM 包版本，以决定使用哪段代码逻辑。如果用户遇到 `InvalidVersion` 错误，可能表示他们安装了开发版或可编辑版的 vLLM 包。在这种情况下，我们提供环境变量 `VLLM_VERSION`，让用户指定要使用的 vLLM 包版本。\n"
"- 文档更改应与最新的 1 到 2 个 vLLM 版本兼容。如有任何重大变更，应添加说明。"

msgid "## Document branch policy"
msgstr "## 文档分支策略"

msgid ""
"To reduce maintenance costs, **all branch documentation content should "
"remain consistent, and version differences can be controlled via variables "
"in the `extra:` block of [mkdocs.yml](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/mkdocs.yml)**. While this is not a simple task, it is a "
"principle we should strive to follow."
msgstr ""
"为降低维护成本，**所有分支的文档内容应保持一致，版本差异可通过 [mkdocs.yml](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/mkdocs.yml) 中 `extra:` "
"块的变量进行控制**。虽然这并非易事，但这是我们应努力遵循的原则。"

msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "说明："

msgid ""
"- `latest` documentation: always points to latest rc release of main branch.\n"
"- `rc version` documentation: there are no further updates after release.\n"
"- `version` documentation: keep updating the `releases/vX.Y.Z` branch documentation to fix doc bugs."
msgstr ""
"- `latest` 文档：始终指向主分支的最新 rc 版本。\n"
"- `rc version` 文档：发布后不再更新。\n"
"- `version` 文档：持续更新 `releases/vX.Y.Z` 分支的文档以修复文档缺陷。"

msgid "## Software dependency management"
msgstr "## 软件依赖管理"

msgid ""
"- `torch-npu`: Ascend Extension for PyTorch (torch-npu) releases a stable version to [PyPI](https://pypi.org/project/torch-npu)\n"
"  every 3 months, a development version (aka the POC version) every month, and a nightly version every day.\n"
"  The PyPI stable version **CAN** be used in vLLM Ascend final version, the monthly dev version **ONLY CAN** be used in\n"
"  vLLM Ascend RC version for rapid iteration, and the nightly version **CANNOT** be used in any vLLM Ascend version or branch."
msgstr ""
"- `torch-npu`：Ascend Extension for PyTorch (torch-npu) 每 3 个月向 [PyPI](https://pypi.org/project/torch-npu) 发布一个稳定版本，每月发布一个开发版本（即 POC 版本），每天发布一个夜间版本。\n"
"  PyPI 稳定版本**可以**用于 vLLM Ascend 最终版本，月度开发版本**仅能**用于 vLLM Ascend RC 版本以进行快速迭代，而夜间版本**不能**用于任何 vLLM Ascend 版本或分支。"

msgid ""
"| vLLM Ascend | vLLM              | Python          | Stable CANN |        "
"PyTorch/torch_npu        |   Triton Ascend   |    Mooncake  |"
msgstr ""
"| vLLM Ascend | vLLM              | Python          | 稳定 CANN   |        "
"PyTorch/torch_npu        |   Triton Ascend   |    Mooncake  |"

msgid ""
"| vLLM Ascend | vLLM         | Python           | Stable CANN | "
